-- Brazil's Verde to have 70 staff after spin-off
-- By Guillermo Parra-Bernal
-- Wed Dec 03, 2014 11:05AM EST
-- None



SAO PAULO, Dec 3 (Reuters) - Verde Asset Management, the spun-off hedge fund venture that will have Credit Suisse Group AG <CSGN.VX> among its partners, expects to start operations in January with 70 people.

